window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is an exclusive, original adventure for the 10th Doctor, read by David Tennant. Featuring additional music and effects, <i>Doctor Who: Dead Air</i> has never been previously published.</p> <p>Hot on the heels of a creature that exists through sound, the Doctor lands on a pirate radio station boat in the late 1960s. The creature has already killed some of the DJs, and the Doctor befriends the survivors. But then the lights go out, and a desperate race for survival begins. Who can the Doctor trust in the dark?</p>"; 
